  "3225420": {
    "name": "冲刺流星 Recharge",
    "steam_appid": 3225420,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推荐使用加速器确保联机稳定，驾驶你的RC遥控赛车与好友一同驰骋赛场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/97d30324806be325c66846794df84965.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/d4f17b922c177abe0d33f000b8a6370f.poster.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/d4f17b922c177abe0d33f000b8a6370f.webm?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/d4f17b922c177abe0d33f000b8a6370f.mp4?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《冲刺流星（Recharge）》中体验前所未有的RC赛车乐趣，这款真正的“sim-cade”游戏将街机的刺激与模拟的操控感相结合。享受逼真的物理效果、出色的画面以及丰富的自定义选项。无论是独自比赛，还是与好友一起征战各类赛道——从职业级RC赛道到灵感源自现实场景的多样化环境——都能让你感受到RC赛车的极致体验。游戏支持多种控制器，包括RC风格的遥控器和游戏手柄，带来动态且真实的RC赛车体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/f9608d151c6c746ee811ff1956fbf346.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/bd43a0baefe9664232e487fa57f82efc.poster.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/bd43a0baefe9664232e487fa57f82efc.webm?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/bd43a0baefe9664232e487fa57f82efc.mp4?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲刺流星（Recharge） 提供单人和多人模式，满足不同玩家的游戏风格。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在单人模式中，你可以与多种难度的AI对手竞速，或者挑战自己的幽灵，突破最佳成绩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人模式支持最多12名玩家在线比赛，既可与朋友创建私人房间，也可进入公共房间与全球玩家同场竞技。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是单人磨炼技巧，还是多人激烈对抗，每个模式都能带来充满激情的竞速体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/1bb6cc0cd7f948337d679b65c80ecabf.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/182812cfea59aa5762ffb49976e2f3d1.poster.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/182812cfea59aa5762ffb49976e2f3d1.webm?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/182812cfea59aa5762ffb49976e2f3d1.mp4?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲刺流星（Recharge）让你可以根据自己的喜好打造独一无二的RC赛车，兼顾性能升级与个性化外观。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过升级电机、ESC和底盘，全面提升赛车的性能，迎接各种挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过喷漆、贴纸和车身等多种定制选项，打造独具风格的赛车外观。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在速度、操控和风格之间找到完美平衡，让每次驾驶都符合你的节奏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/9deca6c065859d06bbe7e86ed13c5354.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/7f5223a30375a81bb7d6766b77fa9ecb.poster.avif?t=1766247377\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/7f5223a30375a81bb7d6766b77fa9ecb.webm?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225420/extras/7f5223a30375a81bb7d6766b77fa9ecb.mp4?t=1766247377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲刺流星（Recharge） 提供多样化的赛道设计，每条赛道都能带来与众不同的RC赛车体验。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在灵感来源于真实RC赛道的职业级赛道上驰骋。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在海滩、游乐园、滑板公园等现实生活场景中体验赛车的乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每条赛道都拥有独特的挑战，带来不断更新的竞速体验，让你一次又一次重返赛道。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 简体中文, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 匈牙利语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 捷克语, 繁体中文",
